{"tid":2422401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"激過唯一反對派鄭松泰？　何俊賢鬧陳茂波「暴君」　麥美娟：羅致光醜唔醜","createTime":"2021-02-25T07:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T06:42:46.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a70b5e2536f128c7876ce510de8e8da785bf253c","tid":2422401,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/dog-16_Ibwxp_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fdog-16_Ibwxp_1200x0.png&h=6b0ea456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波昨（24日）發布新一份財政預算案，今日出席立法會財委會會議回應議員提問。多名建制派勞工界議員對政府未有推出失業援助金大表失望，工聯會麥美娟更批評政府不斷製造貧窮，但勞福局局長以取消強積金對沖要脅，無心解決貧窮問題，斥羅「醜唔醜」。民建聯何俊賢則批評預算案完全無措施支援漁農界，質疑陳茂波有否了解行業需要，形容陳猶如「暴君」拒聽意見。<br />\n<br />\n麥美娟指，國家一直提倡「脫貧攻堅」，但港府不斷製造貧窮，勞福局更無心解決貧窮問題，以取消強積金對沖要脅勞工界，需要公開譴責，斥責羅致光「醜唔醜」；她又強調強積金是退休保障，不可以因為勞福局「唔做嘢」就以強積金去解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波：失業借貸計劃要顧及防止濫用<br />\n她又說，政府百分百擔保的失業貸款計劃未能涵蓋開工不足、被停工、減薪的市民，促請當局放寬申請資格，陳茂波指，失業借貸計劃要顧及防止濫用問題，能否放寬申請資格要審慎考慮；貸款「初心」是幫助有需要人士，若要包括開工不足的市，情況比較複雜，而勞工福局已提高收入不足家庭援助。<br />\n勞聯潘兆平亦要求政府延長計劃申請期限，陳茂波則說計劃暫定為期半年，目前政府研判本港經濟在年中逐漸恢復，相信失業壓力會得到緩解，是否延長計劃期限是言之過早。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/預算案質詢-激過唯一反對派鄭松泰-何俊賢鬧陳茂波-暴君-麥美娟-羅致光醜唔醜/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E8%B3%AA%E8%A9%A2-%E6%BF%80%E9%81%8E%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0-%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%8A%E8%B3%A2%E9%AC%A7%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2-%E6%9A%B4%E5%90%9B-%E9%BA%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%A8%9F-%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89%E9%86%9C%E5%94%94%E9%86%9C%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=0cab1dfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E8%B3%AA%E8%A9%A2-%E6%BF%80%E9%81%8E%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0-%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%8A%E8%B3%A2%E9%AC%A7%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2-%E6%9A%B4%E5%90%9B-%E9%BA%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%A8%9F-%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89%E9%86%9C%E5%94%94%E9%86%9C%2F&h=939bc73b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/預算案質詢-激過唯一反對派鄭松泰-何俊賢鬧陳茂波-暴君-麥美娟-羅致光醜唔醜/</a>"},{"pid":"c2a2bd7c18a5bb905577705dca3acf92ca4ed842","tid":2422401,"uid":254383,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:18:39.000Z","msg":"扯貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d567ab678982041c946735264f0ffb92c2010f82","tid":2422401,"uid":41116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"無左飯民要一人分飾兩角"},{"pid":"003adb151f2ac878654364577bb914a031df4473","tid":2422401,"uid":30070,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:19:35.000Z","msg":"粗口娟好博命交戲"},{"pid":"3f53fe568f7f1a7f6b5d0060ea7f09f4901a4988","tid":2422401,"uid":218731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"最後咪又係通過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363fbf4cc700c15a70cc3e0c96ef2f31dbe86869","tid":2422401,"uid":19437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:21:11.000Z","msg":"講粗口打冷D FRIEND<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32459318842194271805e8fe23435968da94ad79","tid":2422401,"uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:21:44.000Z","msg":"佢暴君咁林鄭係乜?"},{"pid":"c10326fc5663041e3c3f23177c75b0c120720de3","tid":2422401,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"屌完都係支持"},{"pid":"3556acb0f41a2e81c10ce60346a25832593eab7b","tid":2422401,"uid":99962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32459318842194271805e8fe